                <p class="sub-title pad-bt15">The third session of the module motivated us to look at fashion from a whole special perspective. Our session with Mr. Kevin Oliver exposed us to the different aspects of fashion. The discussion ranged from fashion weeks to fashion shows and fashion capitals across the world. Understanding the world of fashion and the influence it has on our lives was the highlight of this session. Needless to say, it was a delightful session which kept us on our toes the entire time and revealed a whole new aspect of the fashion industry. 
                </p>

                <p class="sub-title pad-bt15">Through this module, we were able to gain an understanding of the various cultures around the globe and further help us in developing collaboration and cooperation, dispelling negative stereotypes and personal biases about different groups and recognizing and respecting ways of being that are not our own.  
                </p>

